    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><rs key="#Testamentum">Testamentum</rs> factum per <persName
                            key="#childOf #marriage #parentOf #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"
                                ><name ref="Gherardus/Boreli">Gerardum Boreli</name></persName> de
                        uno <rs key="#Mansi">manso</rs> terre posito in loco qui dicitur
                            <placeName>Corte</placeName> et unum in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/2416">Canule</placeName>. Numero VI. In nomine domini
                        nostri Yhesu Christi. <rs key="#Breve/memoratorium">Brevis recordationis
                            cartula</rs> future recordationis causa, qualiter <persName
                            key="#parentOf">Girardus Borelli</persName> quondam <rs key="#childOf"
                            >filius</rs> in sua ultima disposuit voluntate. Presentibus pluribus
                        hominibus ibique astantibus, dixit atque firmavit <persName key="#marriage"
                                ><name ref="Matilda">Mathildam</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">uxorem</rs> suam usumfructum habere omnium suarum rerum
                        mobilium et immobilium seu familiis quandiu vixerit vel si secundas non
                        contraxerit nuptias. Duas filias suas, scilicet <persName key="#childOf"
                                ><name ref="Gerburga">Girburga</name></persName> seu <persName
                            key="#childOf"><name ref="Berta">Berta</name></persName>, proprietatem
                        predictarum rerum posite infra <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/161"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/53">Parmensis</placeName></geogName> vel <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/193"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/191">Regensi</placeName></geogName> atque <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/124"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/59">Veronensi</placeName></geogName>, eo vero tenore ut
                        si liberis hominibus se copulaverint et filios ex legiptimo matrimonio
                        habueirint et si servis vel libertinis seu familiis se coniunxerint non
                        amplius ex mea substantia habeant unaqueque nisi mansum unum, scilicet
                        Girburga mansum quem <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">rectum et laboratum seu
                            detentum</rs> est per <persName><name ref="Stephanus/Scurtagata"
                                >Stephanum Scurtagata</name></persName> in loco qui dicitur Corte,
                        Berte vero habeat mansum unum que detentum est per <persName><name
                                ref="Benedictus">Benedictum</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Ioahnnes">Iohannem</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">germanos</rs> in corte Canule. Et si hoc evenerit ut
                        predicte filie sine legiptimis filiis ut supra legitur mortue fuerint,
                        suprascripte res proprietario iure deveniant ad <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti
                            et Sancti Simeonis</orgName>, exceptis infrascriptis mansis. Et si una
                        ex sine herede mortua fuerit, pars ipsius non ad sororem sed ad predictum
                        monasterium deveniat. Et insuper liceat Mathilde uxori mee una cum
                                <persName><name ref="Wido/presbiter">Vuido</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Teuperga/de Monteclo">Teuperge</name></persName> de loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/2410">Monteclo</placeName> ex ipsis rebus
                        vendere si debitum ei apparverit quod aliter persolvere non potuerit. Actum
                        est hoc in loco suprascripto <placeName ref="#places/4413">Sancti
                            Benedicti</placeName>. Anni Domini millesimo septuagesimo sexto, septimo
                        idus februarii, indictione quartadecima. + Ego Vuido presbiter prepositus
                        manu mea firmavi. (S.) Ego <persName><name ref="Maginfredus/iudex"
                                >Malnfredus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> interfui. (S.) Ego <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes/legis doctor">Iohannes</name></persName> legis doctor
                        interfui. Omnia autem ut supra legitur acta sunt <rs key="#Witness">in
                            presentia</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Atto">Attonis</name></persName> filii <persName><name
                                ref="Ubericus">Uberici</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Bezo/de Corte Nova">Bezonis</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Corte Nova</placeName>, <persName><name ref="Raginbaldus"
                                >Rambaldi</name></persName> seu <persName><name ref="Vuibertus"
                                >Vuiberti</name></persName> atque <persName><name ref="Rigerius"
                                >Rigerii</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Vuibertus/de Bibianello">Vuiberti</name></persName> da
                            <placeName ref="#places/2468">Bibianello</placeName> etiam
                                <persName><name ref="Bernardus/de Burbasio"
                            >Barnardo</name></persName> da <placeName ref="#places/482"
                            >Burbasio</placeName> et <persName><name ref="Albitius"
                            >Albizio</name></persName> atque <persName><name ref="Turisendus"
                                >Turisindo</name></persName> namque <persName><name ref="Wilibertus"
                                >Vilbertus</name></persName> de <persName><name ref="Gausbertus"
                                >Gosberto</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes/de Ingezo">Iohannis</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name ref="Ingitius">Ingezo</name></persName>. Ego
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes/notarius">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> duas cartas in uno tenore conscripsi. </ab>
